      <title>卡塔尔投资局计划投资 Ardian 半导体</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/qatar-investment-authority-plans-ardian-semiconductor-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡塔尔投资局计划对Ardian Semiconductor进行锚定投资，Ardian Semiconductor是法国私募股权公司Ardian设立的基金，旨在投资整个欧洲的半导体行业。]]></description>
