      <title>美银表示，美国介入提振日元将冒全球风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/bofa-says-it-d-take-global-risks-for-us-to-step-in-to-buoy-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行表示，如果美国与日本协调努力以支撑陷入困境的日元，那么全球金融体系将面临广泛的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/bofa-says-it-d-take-global-risks-for-us-to-step-in-to-buoy-yen</guid>
